              <span class="tech-badge">Next.js</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">Node.js</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">Socket.io</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">MongoDB</span>
            </div>
            <p class="portfolio-card-desc">
              Comprehensive digital solution for armed forces personnel featuring welfare schemes, emergency alerts,
              grievance handling, and a community marketplace. Implemented real-time emergency notifications and
              GPS-based location sharing using Socket.io.
            </p>
            <div class="portfolio-card-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/ArvindSagar65" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="portfolio-card">
            <h3>Home Server Infrastructure</h3>
            <div class="tech-tags" style="margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0;">
              <span class="tech-badge">Ubuntu Server</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">Nginx</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">Tailscale</span>
            </div>
            <p class="portfolio-card-desc">
              Architected a personal lab environment using Ubuntu Live Server to host web services and internal tools.
              Configured Nginx reverse proxy for efficient traffic routing and SSL management. Integrated Tailscale
              mesh networking for secure, encrypted remote access.
            </p>
            <div class="portfolio-card-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/ArvindSagar65" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
