              <span class="tech-badge">Express</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">JavaScript</span>
            </div>
            <p class="portfolio-card-desc">
              Event management platform for campus logistics and technical evaluations. Optimized backend routes
              for participant data retrieval and test result processing.
            </p>
            <div class="portfolio-card-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/ArvindSagar65" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
