      <div>
        <h3>Competitions & Hackathons</h3>
        <div class="competitions-list">
          <div class="competition-item">
            <div class="item-header">
              <span class="item-title">University CTF 2024 — Binary Badlands</span>
              <span class="item-meta">HackTheBox</span>
            </div>
            <p class="item-detail">
              Secured <strong>410th rank out of 1200+</strong> teams in an international competitive hacking tournament. Focus on cybersecurity challenges.
