              <span class="item-meta">Jan 2025 – Present</span>
            </div>
            <p class="item-detail">
              SOSC – Sahyadri Open Source Community. Managing event logistics, technical workshops, and participant engagement for the annual flagship tech fest.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="competition-item">
            <div class="item-header">
              <span class="item-title">Core Team Member — GDG On Campus SCEM</span>
              <span class="item-meta">Sep 2025 – Present</span>
            </div>
